    <abstract>
      <t>   This document lists a set of general requirements for active OAM
   protocols in the Geneve overlay network.  Based on these
   requirements, the IP encapsulation of active Operations,
   Administration, and Maintenance protocols in the Geneve protocol is
   defined.  Considerations for using ICMP and UDP-based protocols are
   discussed.

	 </t>
